And just as a reminder
of what we've even done,

00:04:46.975 --> 00:04:50.642
the first part we shifted
three to the right

00:04:51.508 --> 00:04:54.175
and now we are shifting four up.

00:04:55.553 --> 00:04:58.553
So now, now we are shifting four up.

00:05:01.313 --> 00:05:03.813
So before, y equaled zero here

00:05:05.068 --> 00:05:07.886
